  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK508">
<l>tērāṉ piṟaṉait teḷintāṉ vaḻimuṟai</l>
<l>tīrā viṭumpai tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Sorrow that will not leave even his posterity will come upon him chooses a stranger whose character he has not known.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
